title: Mimosa / Ping Pong Records WMC 09 Promo mix
description:
An exclusive promo mix for WMC 09 consisting of present and soon to be released tracks from the Mimosa and Ping Pong labels.

Featuring tracks from Samuel Lawrence & Roderick T., Unus Emre, Edmund, and Genetikal Twins.

Play it loud!!!

Compiled and Mixed by Samuel Lawrence and Roderick T.

Tracklist...

2.  Samuel Lawrence feat Hot Rod - Tundra (Samuel's Rolling Dub) Ping Pong
